**Aswynn****, Freya** — *Leaves of Yggdrasil* (1990). Ver: Bibliografia **Paxson, Diana L.** — *Taking Up the Runes* (2005). Ver: Bibliografia **Thorsson, Edred** (Stephen E. Flowers) — *Futhark: A Handbook of Rune Magic* (1984). Ver: Bibliografia

